com.tailf.maapi

Interface ResultTypeTag

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ResultType

    public interface ResultTypeTag
extends ResultType

    XPath Result in ConfXMLParam format. This is specified trough ReslutType.class as a parameter to Maapi.queryStart(int,String,String,int,int,List,Class)

    Example: 

      QueryResult qR4 =
      maapi.queryStart(th,"/mtest/servers/server[ip='1.2.3.4']",
                       "/",3,1,
                       Arrays.asList("name",
                                     "ip",
                                     "port"),
                       ResultTypeTag.class);
  for(QueryResult.Entry entry : qR4){
      List rsValue = entry.value();
      for(ResultTypeTag typ: rsValue){
          ConfXMLParam v0 = typ.tag();
          System.out.println("tag :" + v0);
      }
  }
